{"tid":1827330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（重開）文宣 x 包裝","createTime":"2020-01-17T01:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T12:20:30.000Z","uid":325840,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d3eb3a6b979eb024cd433c42b8c09b5da3dd013f","tid":1827330,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T01:25:58.000Z","msg":"永續文宣條件：<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">依家吹雞都係手足去？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1.擴大文宣圈子，溫層淺黃都可以參與</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">手足自己俾錢貼文宣，好蝕？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2.需要搵途徑賺回文宣物資成本</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">連儂地方有限制，被捕成本高？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3.彷效黃色經濟圈，將貼文宣合法化</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">內容開始悶又單一？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">4.要改變內容，參考呢個po</span><br />\n悲情國際文宣已經開始過時<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824457\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824457</a><br />\n<br />\n點樣可以滿足以上要求？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將文宣用作包裝銷售</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n搞手可以係深黃淺黃中立淺藍，賺到錢繼續投資印文宣落包裝，消費者對象（老闆）係深黃淺黃，文宣對象係藍絲中立撚淨睇就夠買埋最好，文宣地點唔再局限於連儂牆，文宣方式唔再局限「貼」，文宣物料唔再局限於紙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好多人屌人血饅頭？</span></span><br />\n首先認清何謂人血饅頭，指借別人上位獲利，代價卻由對方一方承受<br />\n<br />\n即係消費完無相應行動回贈落呢場運動，但印製行程表落包裝係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳遊行</span></span>就唔同淨係貼光復香港時代革命<br />\n<br />\n依家一份文宣成本10蚊內，搞手標價紙巾口罩10蚊內宣傳埋，咁算唔算人血饅頭？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無人買就無文宣效果？</span></span><br />\n手足買個口罩紙巾都係幾蚊，賣出唔難，孝子可以買定幾卷講警暴嘅廁紙返屋企用<br />\n<br />\n對藍絲，係包裝設計入手，如果佢淨睇唔買已經達到文宣效果（我地依家都係不斷扔錢印野求佢地望下，分別係印落紙無回報）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做網店藍絲接觸唔到？</span></span><br />\n建議搵黃店合作，賣紙巾外賣餐具墊枱紙紙袋俾佢地，再諗遠啲可以係黃店記號，唔建議用派，除非成本好撚平同紙差唔多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係幾想俾非同路人賺錢？</span></span><br />\n同黃色經濟圈一樣，只要佢繼續出產，都係幫手做緊宣傳，最緊要參與度高<br />\n***藍絲做搞手係BONUS，文宣同佢盤生意掛勾，文宣幾勁盤生意就幾好，直接入腦，而且迫咗佢地對外轉立場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣內容好似廢廢地無用買唔買？</span></span><br />\n做個精明消費者，搞手有責任謹慎選擇文宣內容，但宣傳721 831呢啲實無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點監督防止「落格」？</span></span><br />\n好現實，要知道賺錢係推動運動嘅其中一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誘因</span></span>，同埋背後人工都係錢，達致文宣效果又唔太貴就理撚得佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">最後，好想做但驚呢門生意成本好貴？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n老實講我都係紙上談兵非專業，具體細節如批發商、產品牌子、文宣內容、銷售點、銷售方式都需要再諗，但開po嘅用意係想講呢條橋work會幫到文宣路之餘仲可以連繫黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n少少建議係，第一次要眾籌，選擇產品成本過高都唔應該考慮，建議以消耗品或其包裝為主，因為有一定購買力，文宣內容流動性高，又平，其後有本錢先再諗。產品選擇有以下建議：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DW6B92C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDW6B92C.jpg&h=3f514a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FifrNPi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFifrNPi.jpg&h=39073706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：小弟純粹發夢，未做過搞手唔知有幾難，想拋下磚引下玉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推到有文宣組做</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d33f84cd58473aec1d92cf8a7fb08f5bb0e2eb0","tid":1827330,"uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T01:59:25.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"3fde909373d66fa7e0186a1c9e782777111f8c55","tid":1827330,"uid":135277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:17:13.000Z","msg":"Help u push"},{"pid":"6d7192418f071c6fa72d1485b9d3c432e1eda6c9","tid":1827330,"uid":149682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba70f94b0c65811ecc62bbd32faaf2dbf9748645","tid":1827330,"uid":149682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"將文宣滲透生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee93e989565fd1237a840d0a92691ff304bdbe5","tid":1827330,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:54:39.000Z","msg":"要眾籌出聲"},{"pid":"5cbcb7cb2f5574f5dd2a13c1aa55dd6f107942fc","tid":1827330,"uid":217873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遵理要加入藍店名單</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmtYdFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmtYdFU.jpg&h=17daae5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6586fbef3fc43ab696033fb0022d06a66021ec1c","tid":1827330,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b22a1e40fd66c5b023f42af6fe1febe3a9432ab3","tid":1827330,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}